        ' To create a voucher, you would need to have cards with funds.
        ' Since easy.money wouldn’t allow for currency conversion directly
        ' in the platform (it redirects the user to Uphold),
        ' we opted to apply a filter that would only show the cards with funds available.
        ' The user could still choose to see all his cards,
        ' but if he selected one with no funds a modal would pop-up
        | explaining he could either select another card or deposit money through his Uphold account.
